<section id="about" class="section">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">About <em>me</em></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div>
        <img
          src="/images/tina.jpg"
          alt="Tina Ohanian"
          class="about-photo"
          onerror="this.outerHTML='<div class=\'about-photo-ph\'>images/tina.jpg</div>'"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="about-content">
        <div class="about-block">
          <p class="about-block-label">Bio</p>
          <p>
            Tina Ohanian is a presentation designer focused on pitch decks, visual
            storytelling, and branded sales materials within sports and
            entertainment. Her work centers on creating polished, executive-ready
            presentations that translate ideas, scripts, and concepts into clear
            visual narratives. With a background in marketing and partnerships, she
            brings both strategic thinking and strong layout sensibility to every
            project.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-block">
          <p class="about-block-label">My approach</p>
          <p>
            My approach to design begins with understanding the story behind each
            project — its tone, audience, and creative intent. I focus on building
            clean visual systems, strong typography, and cohesive layouts that
            support narrative rather than distract from it. Collaboration and
            iteration are central to my process, and I value feedback as a tool to
            refine and elevate the final presentation. Whether preparing a pitch
            deck or sales presentation, my goal is to create materials that feel
            polished, purposeful, and visually aligned with the project's identity.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
